msgstr "Détermine quelles parties sont visibles après les démarrage."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:102
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Save last position, size and panel settings</guilabel>: When "
#| "launched, &krusader; resizes itself to the size it was when last shut-"
#| "down. &krusader; also appears in the same location on the screen, having "
#| "panels sorted and aligned as they were. If this option is unchecked, you "
