msgstr "Vous pouvez configurer ici les modes de sélection."

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1116
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Viewer opens each file in a separate window</guilabel>: you can "
#| "use the browsing tabs for navigation."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Internal editor and viewer opens each file in separate window</"
